    <item>
      <title>本田推出升级版 Freed 小型货车，包括双电机混合动力车</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/honda-launches-updated-freed-minivan-including-two-motor-hybrid</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本田汽车公司在日本推出了 Freed 小型货车的升级版，其中包括一款双电机混合动力车，尽管纯电动汽车需求放缓，但这款车仍越来越受欢迎。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/honda-launches-updated-freed-minivan-including-two-motor-hybrid</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 04:14:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>软银将投资人工智能初创公司 Perplexity，估值达 30 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/softbank-to-invest-in-perplexity-in-ai-race-against-google-rivals</link>
      <description><![CDATA[软银集团旗下的愿景基金 2 号正在以 30 亿美元的估值投资美国人工智能初创公司 Perplexity AI，这是孙正义对该领域的最新押注，他认为该领域对于确保自己的遗产至关重要。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/softbank-to-invest-in-perplexity-in-ai-race-against-google-rivals</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 04:07:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚马逊计划推出折扣网店以对抗中国的 Temu 和 Shein</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-27/amazon-plans-discount-web-store-to-counter-china-s-temu-shein</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚马逊公司计划推出一个在线店面，销售从中国直接发货的低价服装和家居用品。这家总部位于西雅图的电子商务巨头旨在对抗 Temu 和 Shein 等折扣新贵的崛起。Annabelle Droulers 在彭博电视台报道。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-27/amazon-plans-discount-web-store-to-counter-china-s-temu-shein</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 03:57:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>SpaceX 的投标报价据称将使该公司估值达到创纪录的 2100 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/spacex-tender-offer-said-to-value-company-at-record-210-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，SpaceX 将通过招标方式以每股 112 美元的价格出售内部人士股份，这一高于预期的价格将使埃隆马斯克的太空和卫星公司的价值接近 2100 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/spacex-tender-offer-said-to-value-company-at-record-210-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 03:32:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美光的抛售凸显了人工智能预期过高的风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/micron-s-selloff-shows-risk-of-sky-high-ai-expectations</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美光科技公司业绩公布后的抛售再次提醒全球投资者，投资人工智能芯片制造商存在一定风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/micron-s-selloff-shows-risk-of-sky-high-ai-expectations</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 02:26:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>现代汽车寻求更多电动汽车改装，推出售价低于 25,000 欧元的 Inster City 汽车</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/hyundai-seeks-more-ev-converts-with-sub-25-000-inster-city-car</link>
      <description><![CDATA[现代汽车公司正加入试图加速电动汽车普及、抵御来自中国的低成本竞争的汽车制造商行列，推出一款电池供电的车型，据称其售价将低于 25,000 欧元（26,775 美元）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/hyundai-seeks-more-ev-converts-with-sub-25-000-inster-city-car</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 00:45:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚马逊云计算部门会议因加沙抗议活动而中断</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/amazon-cloud-unit-conference-interrupted-by-protest-over-gaza</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚马逊公司云计算部门主办的一场会议遭到抗议者的干扰，抗议者要求终止亚马逊与以色列政府以及 Alphabet Inc. 旗下谷歌之间共享的价值 12 亿美元的合同。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/amazon-cloud-unit-conference-interrupted-by-protest-over-gaza</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 23:28:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Anduril 的 15 亿美元交易凸显了风险投资对国防科技的热情</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/anduril-s-1-5-billion-deal-underscores-vc-zeal-for-defense-tech</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，Anduril Industries Inc. 正在与彼得·泰尔 (Peter Thiel) 的创始人基金及其他投资者进行洽谈，以筹集 15 亿美元，这将成为今年规模最大的非专注于人工智能领域的融资轮次之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/anduril-s-1-5-billion-deal-underscores-vc-zeal-for-defense-tech</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 23:24:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>FBI 明星合作者可能一直在实施新的诈骗</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-06-26/jpmorgan-hacker-may-have-built-new-fraud-empire-while-working-with-fbi</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当臭名昭著的摩根大通黑客事件的策划者 Gery Shalon 叛变时，美国执法部门认为这是一次胜利。但新证据表明，Shalon 在与 FBI 合作期间，在欧洲建立了一个庞大的新欺诈帝国。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-06-26/jpmorgan-hacker-may-have-built-new-fraud-empire-while-working-with-fbi</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 21:00:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美光股价因预测未达到预期而下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/micron-falls-after-forecast-fails-to-meet-lofty-expectations</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国最大的计算机内存芯片制造商美光科技公司 (Micron Technology Inc.) 股价在尾盘交易中下跌，原因是其预测令寻求从人工智能狂热中获得更多回报的投资者感到失望。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/micron-falls-after-forecast-fails-to-meet-lofty-expectations</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 20:08:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
